<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>SmileTalk 投稿修正完了</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --main-color: #b79fcb;
      --main-color-dark: #a487c0;
      --soft-color: #f2edf7;
    }
    body { margin:0; font-family:sans-serif; background:#faf7fc; }
    header { background-color: var(--main-color); padding: 15px 0; text-align:center; }
    header .site-title { font-family:'Pacifico', cursive; font-size:2rem; color:#fff; margin:0; text-shadow:0 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .page-wrapper { max-width:600px; margin:40px auto 80px auto; text-align:center; }
    .custom-card { border-radius:12px; border:1px solid #e8e2f0; box-shadow:0 3px 6px rgba(183,159,203,0.15); padding:40px 20px; background:#fff; }
    .btn-custom { background-color: var(--main-color); border:none; color:#fff; padding:10px 20px; border-radius:6px; cursor:pointer; transition:0.2s; font-family:'Pacifico', cursive; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block; margin-top:20px; }
    .btn-custom:hover { background-color: var(--main-color-dark); }
    footer { margin-top:40px; background-color: var(--soft-color); padding:10px 0; text-align:center; color:#7a6a8c; font-size:0.9rem; }
    .message { color:#6c4e89; font-size:1.2rem; margin-bottom:20px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1 class="site-title">SmileTalk</h1>
  </header>

  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <div class="custom-card">
      <p class="message">投稿は修正されました。</p>
      <a href="/static_pages/thread_index" class="btn btn-custom">投稿一覧に戻る</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    SmileTalk © 2025
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
